<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="id794107cc-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior section 22 of act <date date="1938-06-21">June 21, 1938</date>, was renumbered section 24 and is classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t15/s717u">section 717u of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
